msgstr "一个可运行的 *本地* 容器环境： link:https://docs.docker.com/get-started/get-docker/[Docker] 还是 link:https://podman.io/docs/installation[Podman]"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/compose-dev-services.adoc
#, fuzzy
