msgstr "Compose 工具，例如 `docker-compose` 或 `podman-compose` （请注意 `，docker compose` 和 `podman compose` 命令在内部会调用这些二进制文件）："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/compose-dev-services.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For Docker: https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/[Installing Docker Compose]"
msgstr "关于 Docker： link:https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/[安装 Docker Compose]"

#. type: Plain text
